snippet.textDisplay:
What's with the "Jhoole Laal" stuff in between the song after the "Dama Dam"? I'm always waiting for the "Mast kalandar" to drop but she just pauses halfway and it just feels wierd, abrupt and unsatisfying.... 
I feel like they are trying way too hard to try "different" things with each and every song, but it just doesn't seem to be working. I mean, what's the point of completely removing the famous chorus of the song for which it is known for? It just doesn't make sense to me. I just don't see the point behind it.
 This song, while there wasn't anything particularly bad about it, in fact, it was good, but ultimately it just felt unsatisfying.
